  Added patch for iptables-restore. Contributed by fridtjof@fbunet.de in #10736.

  25 Sep 2002; Daniel Ahlberg <aliz@gentoo.org> files/iptables-1.2.7a-imq.diff-3 :
  Closes #8046.

